* '''Sir Tristram:''' Hail Arthur, King of the Britons!
* '''Player:''' Um... Hello.
* '''Sir Tristram:''' Thanks for freeing Merlin.
* '''Player:''' No problem. It was easy.
* {{tact|end}}

===Sir Pelleas===
* '''Sir Pelleas:''' Greetings to the court of King Arthur!
* '''Sir Pelleas:''' You are a very talented Knight indeed to have freed Merlin so quickly. You have all of our gratitude.
* {{tact|end}}

