* '''Sir Gawain:''' Good day to you!
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|Good day.}}
** '''Player:''' Good day.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Know you of any quests sir knight?}}
** '''Player:''' Know you of any quests sir knight?
** '''Sir Gawain:''' I think you've done the main quest we were on right now...
** '''Sir Gawain:''' Good day to you!
** {{tact|end}}

